articles.description: A long string of actresses, with replicas of the outfits she wore in (sometimes questionable) fluffed wigs, have charted the "greatest hits" of Diana's royal life. Now Kristen Stewart joins their ranks, writes Giselle Bastin.
articles.content: Since the earliest Princess Diana biopics appeared soon after the royal wedding in 1981, there have been repeated attempts to bring to the screen the story of Diana's journey from blue-blooded ingenu… [+5378 chars]
